1. Downlaod Instant Player 2019 file from the following url
ftp://ftp.igd.fraunhofer.de/outgoing/irbuild/Ubuntu-18-x86_64/InstantReality-Ubuntu-18.04-x64-2.15.0.52878rc1.deb

2. apt install gdebi

3. Install on the machine using the following command on terminal
sudo gdebi  <downloaded_file.deb>


The program gets installed and on a successful install you can find
file at the location /opt/instantReality/bin

# install the license
sudo mv /opt/instantReality/bin/license.xml default_license.xml
sudo cp 2019_IR-license.xml /opt/instantReality/bin/license.xml


